crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/ims"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET POLICY HTTP traffic on port 443 (POST)
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET 443 (msg:"ET POLICY HTTP traffic on port 443 (POST)"; flow:to_server,established; http.method; content:"POST"; http.header; content:!".etrade.com|3a|443|0d 0a|"; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:2013926; rev:10; metadata:attack_target Client_Endpoint, tls_state plaintext, created_at 2011_11_18, deployment Perimeter, confidence High, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2024_03_12;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: SURICATA HTTP Request unrecognized authorization method
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http any any -> any any (msg:"SURICATA HTTP Request unrecognized authorization method"; flow:established,to_server; app-layer-event:http.request_auth_unrecognized; flowint:http.anomaly.count,+,1; classtype:protocol-command-decode; sid:2221034; rev:1;)
